<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />"Yahweh, make me know when will be the end of my life</para>

<para style="q1">and the extent of my days.</para>

<para style="q1">Show me how transient I am.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />See, you have made my days only the width of my hand,</para>

<para style="q1">and my lifetime is like nothing before you.</para>

<para style="q1">Surely every man is a single breath.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
